Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.33,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:36.24,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}In the Midst of Turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:40.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:43.35,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! You have to hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:47.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't "have to" listen to a word that \Ncomes out of you royals' filthy mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:51.07,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Melty-sama, His Majesty calls for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.01,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.11,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:58.91,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.08,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:01.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.60,flashback,Mirelia,0000,0000,0000,,Melty, I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.56,flashback,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.06,flashback,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:28.41,flashback,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,and admonish the king for his unjust \Ntreatment of the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.86,flashback,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, I would go myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.82,flashback,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:45.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least have\Ngiven her a chance to speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.05,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:49.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.32,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you so cold to Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:52.82,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.02,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't play with her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking as a father would isn't \Ngoing to help Filo understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.25,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan hasn't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.92,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.63,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.34,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Mel-san \Nis royalty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust them. Any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.04,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:58.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Quit peeking and just come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.34,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You have visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.00,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.60,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.81,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:16.86,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us accompany you, \Nat least during the Waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:22.32,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We were deeply touched by the \Nway you fought in the last Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.53,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here wants to support your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you were looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.87,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:34.71,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We'd decided to ask you the next time \Nwe saw you here in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you just want to fight the Waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you can do that without following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:43.34,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No, we want to fight with you,\N Sir Shield Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And what's your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.22,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We're all from the village of Lute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.52,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you saved our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.24,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,So we want to help you in any way we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.61,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We want to repay you for saving \Nour fellow villagers' lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Buy this for 150 silver pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll consider your offer if \Nyou can cough up the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can gain my trust by buying this off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.97,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred and fifty silver pieces, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.05,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.97,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to arrange it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.72,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.10,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go gather the money right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:38.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're pressuring them to \Nbuy a leftover accessory for that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.65,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You never change, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.89,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fix these up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.75,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,The made-to-order stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:01.13,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I throw in some freebie materials, \Nit'll cost you around this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see an asterisk next to \Ntheir level indicators now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:13.02,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are ready for class upgrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Class upgrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.56,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,It lets you increase your level cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.36,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Only those recognized by the \Ncourt even have the option,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.40,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess you are a hero, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.61,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,You choose what path to take \Nwhen you upgrade your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.07,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of trouble deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.37,sign_11287_85_Class_Upgrade,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(188,188)}Class Upgrade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:35.01,sign_11308_85_Class_Upgrade_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(396,1)}Class Upgrade
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it at the dragon hourglass, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of upgrade do you want, Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with whatever you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Decide your future path yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:49.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,After the Waves are over, \NI'll go back to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So pick something that'll help \Nyou survive without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're going back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take a skewer, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.18,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.11,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.22,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.03,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.70,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen gold pieces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.86,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,A class upgrade costs fifteen \Ngold pieces per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.58,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.78,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I could get thousands \Nof ten rolls for that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, you go ahead and upgrade first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.38,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it the next \Ntime we come. Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen gold pieces, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.98,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,Our apologies. We seem \Nto have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.94,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,We are forbidden from providing \Nupgrades to the Shield Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But they just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.12,main,Nun,0000,0000,0000,,It's a direct order from His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:13.62,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to sell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Never. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.52,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.44,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your business is thriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.74,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:35.62,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Your traveling trade was very \Nprofitable for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.91,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,First and foremost, your filolial queen \Nhas gained quite the reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.21,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Nobles all across Melromarc
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.79,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,contacted me to ask how they could \Nprocure one for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.75,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Secondly, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.59,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,You've helped my business gain a reputation \Nfor providing high-quality slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.35,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,The money hasn't stopped rolling in since!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.14,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how may I help you today? \NWould you like another slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.73,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you need assistance \Nwith a filolial experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:10.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can you arrange class upgrades for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.93,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Class upgrades, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're refusing to let \Nus do it in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you having a slave \Nthat was over level 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.50,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry to say this,\Nbut we don't provide that service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.96,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,However, worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:36.84,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,You can simply get it done at another \Ncountry's dragon hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:43.18,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Ordinarily, I would \Ncharge for this information,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:48.57,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,but since you're the one asking, \NI'll tell you for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:53.86,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking favorable countries \Nfor you to upgrade classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.57,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,there's Mercenary Nation Zeltoble,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.95,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-Human Country Siltvelt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.33,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,and Shieldfreeden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.37,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend Shieldfreeden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:10.54,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,For a country of demi-humans, \Nit's very welcoming to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.97,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,By ship, two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:17.72,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,And by wagon, a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We won't get there before the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:28.60,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about making do this time by \Nequipping your filolial queen with a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.52,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,A weapon for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.36,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like these wyvern talons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.45,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's a wyvern?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How much are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:42.12,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,In light of your continued patronage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.84,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,I'll offer you a special \Nprice of five gold pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Four. And throw in reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.79,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.83,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,How you've grown into the \Nkind of man I just love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.97,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,You make my spine tingle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.60,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This feels kinda weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.92,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Getting used to them might take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Slave Merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:08.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can we test these talons out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.56,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all the monsters \Nhere are merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.61,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.24,main,ST,0000,0000,0000,,I have just the job request!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.40,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Ew...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This stench is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that slave merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:40.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why would there be monsters \Nin the capital's sewers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:45.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've dumped them here \Nafter they grew too hard to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.01,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:58.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.07,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This sword is really sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.37,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,These talons are awesome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The parts you bandage heal really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days until the Wave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you've recovered by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:52.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:56.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we don't know where \Nthe next Wave will arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:59.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,we have to prepare for \Nanything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:02.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And given the possibility of \Ncasualties in a town or village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:05.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,we should stock up on a ton of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:09.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And we should scout out possible \Ncombat zones and strategize...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Once all the Waves are repelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:22.77,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,you'll go back to your own world, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,May I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.44,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,May I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:33.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.90,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.20,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's being lovey-dovey with Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.08,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You were!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.83,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to kiss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.79,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You were! I saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,God, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have an early start tomorrow! Go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.39,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.23,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What a sad-looking town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The lord here must be a scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That toll told the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If this town was attacked in the Wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.59,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Trade us food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'd honestly prefer money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.96,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.84,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing else left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people not from Melromarc?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:25.14,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. We're refugees from the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.06,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Some adventurer apparently sent from here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:31.10,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,put together a resistance force \Nand started a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.23,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're in this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What was this adventurer like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:38.78,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really know,\Nbut the rumors say he used a bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:44.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Set up an emergency kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:45.87,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:14.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Wave hits in 27 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's grab some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ren and Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:36.09,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,I overthrew a despot in \Nthe country to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.84,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,But when I went to the Guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.92,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,they'd already paid the \Nreward out to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.64,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Same here. Somebody stole \Na job request from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:48.18,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like someone's going \Naround pretending to be us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:49.47,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the daily special,\Nand she'll have a large kids' meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.27,top,G,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.81,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.65,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a Guild request to \Noverthrow a town lord to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.44,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.02,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,From the Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:58.82,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.78,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,From looking into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:04.41,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,it seems that lord is heavily taxing \Ncitizens beyond the court's set limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:09.66,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,using that revenue to hire mercenaries, \Nand suppressing dissent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.16,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy taxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.41,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do they mean that town from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.79,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.87,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,That looks yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.17,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Time to dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.67,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,Chew before you swallow, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:20.71,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.38,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Someone needs to be taught that with\N great power comes great responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.14,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, that's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.60,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just didn't know you'd\Nbeen bitten by a spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.65,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Bitten by a spider?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.36,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.41,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one impersonating us,\Nthen stealing our jobs and rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.03,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Because who else would—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:55.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ever considered that it may be because \Nyou're trying to be a cool, secret vigilante?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.92,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:05.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the "adventurer" who helped \Nthe resistance in the north?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.84,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:11.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happened to that \Ncountry after the king was ousted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.90,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is this everyone from your village?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.69,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.86,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.82,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,After the revolution, \Nour lives did get a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.99,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,But not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:33.20,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Then the resistance started \Nhiking up the taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.37,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.58,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know too much about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.77,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently it takes a lot \Nof money to run a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:45.26,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, maybe the previous \Nking was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All you did was switch up who \Nwas running the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.22,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.57,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about impersonating—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.40,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,How do you explain my case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Was it about some disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.73,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,If you know, that makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.27,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you steal that job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:09.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that the corpse of that \Ndragon you killed caused an epidemic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I got rid of that corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the job request was canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.08,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm lying, go to that \Neastern village and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:23.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how many \Npeople died because of you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.55,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.47,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:37.16,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.81,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,You believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.85,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,He has no reason to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause any more problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.40,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:00.90,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,I embedded that dragon zombie core\N in your chest plate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.71,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,and also gave it an auto-repair function.\NIt's one of my best works.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:04.96,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:09.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just how badly do you want to \Nmake me look like a bandit chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.88,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You look cool, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.64,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That suits you very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.35,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.52,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:23.31,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,We ran around and somehow \Nscraped up 150 silver pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Use that money to get \Nyourselves better equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.53,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you'll accept us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:38.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you guys dropping like flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.70,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:46.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you try to exploit or set me up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have hell to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:49.92,main,Ei,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.63,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for us having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.93,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,We have lots more friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are less than 24 hours until the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a strategy meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.85,top,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:01.68,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Not again, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:05.33,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,My shop isn't your meeting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:13.24,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Melty-sama appears to have made contact \Nwith the Shield Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:16.95,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,If the Shield Hero is the \Nkind of man I hear he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.20,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,reconciliation will take quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.25,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for putting Melty through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.17,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,but this, too, is her duty \Nas the future ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.96,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:29.50,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.75,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.43,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,The next Wave is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.35,main,Mir,0000,0000,0000,,Will the heroes be able to overcome it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.93,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}Catastrophe Returns
